data.description: Situated in the serene Blacksburg area, this property provides a peaceful and private setting while remaining conveniently accessible to local amenities and services. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting living space, providing ample room for relaxation and entertainment. This property presents a unique opportunity to own home with a spacious 2.24 -acre lot and a versatile Workshed. Whether you're a homeowner seeking space and comfort or an enthusiast looking for a workshop, this property caters to a variety of lifestyles. Don't miss your chance to make this your dream home. No septic record provided.
